Joan Ritz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joan_Ritz 0 Joan Ritz (c. 1882 – 6 November 1956) was a British actress of the silent era.She was born Jessie Rihll in West Ham, London, UK and died in Brighton, Sussex, England, UK.
